data.description: Welcome HOME! Sunning 4 bed 2 bath home nestled on a cul-de-sac in the desirable gated GRAND LANDINGS community in Palm Coast.   Step into this spacious open floor, boasting massive ceilings, spacious laundry room, gourmet kitchen with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and custom pantry along side an elegant comfortable Main living space. Large master suite includes a luxurious bath and custom walk-in closet. The property features a 6ft Vinyl fenced yard and a 25ft extended screened lanai for outdoor enjoyment, sprinkler system and Ring Video surveillance through the property. All overlooking a serene conservation area.  Community offers a Pool, Fitness center, illuminated sidewalks, playground & dog park all with a low HOA. Minutes from shopping, dining and Flagler Beach. Our prefer closing agent is JK Closing Attorneys. Buyer can get buyer credit using our prefer lender.
